reviewText: These girls rock,  I'm a huge fan of Hunter Valentine,  loved this DVD of them from years ago. Check them out!

Im a big Hunter Valentine fan and I got this dvd to complete my collection.  Although this dvd is pretty basic with songs from a live performance, its a great must have for everyone that is a fan.  I just wished they had more extras on this.

"Hunter Valentine" is really an awesome and amazing All Girl Band from Tronto/Canada. This DVD "We're Here To Recruit You" is an fabulous production. It's a Must for all fans from Hunter Valentine. Now I wait to the next DVD!!!
